Package com.Akif

Class SkipArrayList<E extends java.lang.Comparable<E>>

java.lang.Object
com.Akif.SkipArrayList<E>
All Implemented Interfaces:
SearchTree<E>
public class SkipArrayList<E extends java.lang.Comparable<E>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements SearchTree<E>
A Skip List where each node in the lowest-level list keeps several elements instead of just one element as in a B-tree node.
